    <item>
      <title>尽管有盈利之路，迪士尼仍因订户前景疲软而下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/disney-reports-lower-streaming-tv-loss-boosts-profit-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华特迪士尼公司(Walt Disney Co.)公布本季度流媒体用户增长前景不温不火，并表示公园参观量预计将从疫情后的峰值水平放缓，该公司股价创下一年半来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/disney-reports-lower-streaming-tv-loss-boosts-profit-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 10:30:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英飞凌首席执行官预计中国电动汽车势头强劲，欧盟将于 2025 年复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/infineon-margin-outlook-misses-as-carmakers-buy-fewer-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英飞凌科技公司首席执行官 Jochen Hanebeck 表示，该公司看到中国汽车行业“非常强劲的势头”，并预计欧洲电动汽车市场明年将复苏，这使得这家德国芯片制造商的股价创下四年来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/infineon-margin-outlook-misses-as-carmakers-buy-fewer-chips</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 05:39:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
